text: St. Paul Street may refer to: *St. Paul Street (Baltimore) in Maryland, United States *St. Paul Street (MBTA Green Line "B" Branch station) in Massachusetts, United States *St. Paul Street (MBTA Green Line "C" Branch station), on the Green Line "C" Branch *Rue Saint-Paul (Montreal) in Montreal, Quebec, Canada *A portion of Niagara Regional Road 81 in Saint Catharines, Ontario, Canada * Rue Saint-Paul (Paris), in Paris, France
